      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor was like 15 mins at the end of a super busy appointment and just handed me the script. i feel fine though. like, if the bacteria are gone, isn't the medicine just doing nothing at this point? feels kinda pointless to keep taking them for another week just for the sake of it.",
