      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i just feel like im overthinking it. my friend had a similar thing and they stopped as soon as they felt better and they were totally fine. plus i have a really sensitive stomach and these pills make me feel nauseous. if there's no more redness or pain, isn't it pretty safe to just call it a day? it seems like a lot of unnecessary side effects for an infection that's already gone.",
